# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# AlgoTrade Pro — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# NEVER commit .env to Git!
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Application ──
APP_ENV=development
DEBUG=false
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:5173

# ── Database ──
# Local:   postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:yourpassword@localhost:5432/algotrade
# Cloud:   postgresql+asyncpg://user:pass@ep-xxx.neon.tech/algotrade?sslmode=require
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://postgres:yourpassword@localhost:5432/algotrade

# ── Authentication ──
# Generate: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(64))"
JWT_SECRET_KEY=CHANGE_ME_GENERATE_A_REAL_SECRET_KEY_AT_LEAST_32_CHARS
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
JWT_EXPIRE_MINUTES=60

# ── Encryption (Credential Vault) ──
# Generate: python -c "from cryptography.fernet import Fernet; print(Fernet.generate_key().decode())"
MASTER_ENCRYPTION_KEY=CHANGE_ME_GENERATE_A_REAL_FERNET_KEY

# ── Broker: Angel One (optional) ──
ANGEL_API_KEY=
ANGEL_CLIENT_ID=
ANGEL_PASSWORD=
ANGEL_TOTP_SECRET=

# ── Broker: Zerodha (optional) ──
ZERODHA_API_KEY=
ZERODHA_API_SECRET=

# ── AI / Search (optional) ──
GEMINI_API_KEY=
TAVILY_API_KEY=

# ── Telegram Bot (optional) ──
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_ALLOWED_USERS=

# ── Rate Limiting ──
RATE_LIMIT_LOGIN=5/minute
RATE_LIMIT_ORDERS=30/minute

# ── Risk Management ──
MAX_ORDER_VALUE=100000
MAX_DAILY_LOSS=5000
MAX_POSITIONS=10
MAX_POSITION_SIZE_PERCENT=20
